Package: plumber.schema
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of JSON Schema for plumber
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Nils",
           family = "Schnakenberg",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "schnakenberg.nils@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Nils Schnakenberg <schnakenberg.nils@gmail.com>
Description: Implementation of JSON Schema for plumber. This package provides a
    function to generate a plumber router from a JSON Schema. The router can be
    used to validate requests against the schema and to generate OpenAPI
    documentation.
